{
  "texts": [
    "First, execution time was normalized to a range between 0 and 1 by dividing the execution time by three times the largest value observed in the GA runs.",
    "This normalization method can be seen as optimistic, ensuring that execution times remain within a desirable range.",
    "On the other hand, diversity was already normalized between 0 and 1.",
    "Given this, more weight was assigned to execution time to avoid it having less importance than diversity.",
    "Additionally, the focus on execution time aligns with the primary goal of optimizing for WCET."
  ]
}